{"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1022, "img_height": 1502, "blocks": [{"box": [758, 184, 787, 469], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["あー、なんか遠い世界だ。"]}, {"box": [636, 184, 661, 444], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["昔の自分も今の自身を"]}, {"box": [576, 184, 601, 522], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["イメージできてなかったけど。"]}, {"box": [451, 184, 476, 394], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["それがもう１年前"]}, {"box": [326, 184, 351, 542], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["救急車に乗ったし。入院したし、"]}, {"box": [200, 183, 228, 429], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["普段は忘れてるけど。"]}, {"box": [696, 183, 725, 646], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["自分とこの街がイメージで結びつかない。"]}, {"box": [384, 181, 416, 699], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["今にして思えばいろいろ辛い時期だったかも。"]}, {"box": [265, 184, 290, 623], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["僕の体にはいまだにに手術跡が残ってる。"]}]}